  <description>
    <p>
      Format Foundry provides conversion, extraction, metadata editing,
      archive handling, media workflows, aria2 downloads, and storage-analysis tools
      in a single desktop application.
    </p>
    <p>
      It is designed for desktop batch workflows where converting, packaging,
      extracting, downloading, and reviewing outputs need to happen in one place.
    </p>
  </description>
